Package: king-pong
Version: 1.1.0-7
Section: games
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: King Alex Gilbert
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-3.0, gir1.2-webkit2-4.1 | gir1.2-webkit2-4.0
Recommends: zenity, gstreamer1.0-plugins-good
Description: King Pong arcade campaign game
 King Pong is a retro Pong-inspired arcade campaign with save slots,
 custom games, local and LAN two-player modes, original music,
 controller support, and a secret boss.
 .
 This compact package uses the distribution-provided WebKitGTK runtime,
 enables GPU rendering, and preserves the original high-DPI game canvas.
